original_title: トルコ１１０番　悶絶くらげ
overview: Nikkatsu Roman Porno film about a brothel headhunter named Miura who brings young runaway Choma to a bathhouse/brothel and begins her prostitution career. Miura also falls in love with Choma, which causes problems when she falls for a dangerous yakuza gangster.
title: Bathhouse 911: Jellyfish Bliss
